'''Władysław Szajnocha''' (1857-1928) was a Polish geologist and paleontologist; son of historian [[Karol Szajnocha]]. Rector of the [[Jagiellonian University]] (1911-1912 and 1916-1917).<ref>[http://www.pgi.gov.pl/muzeum/poczet/Wladyslaw_Szajnocha/wladyslaw_szajnocha.html Halina Urban, Biography of W. Szajnocha], a webpage of the  [[Geological Museum of the State Geological Institute]], [[Warsaw]]</ref>

